_sText:
Pretty awesome fast paced map, would be good for a deathmatch, there is no buyzone in the map but there is still a wide selection of weapons available.

The map is focused on a central arena, in the middle of the arena there is a teleport up into the sniper point where there are also more powerful weapons, and it holds a good view over the whole map, while leaving the sniper well hidden.

Not for less than 4 people, its designed to be a fast paced map, should be great  for deathmatch games...wait did I already mention that?

Extract to cstrike/maps.
